Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:47.05,Sai,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Everyone watching the TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.62,Sai,,0,0,0,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.17,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:54.76,Sai,,0,0,0,,We're doing something special today by\Nbroadcasting a Hikaru no Go side story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:59.89,Sai,,0,0,0,,It will show Hikaru when he was in the 7th grade, back when he was still cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:01.60,Sai,,0,0,0,,So look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:02.94,Sai,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:07.07,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'll be... just as cool as ever of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:09.94,Sai,,0,0,0,,After all I am the MAIN CHARACTER!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.99,Sai,,0,0,0,,Well then, enjoy the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:21.33,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(345,115)}The Sixty-Fourth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:21.33,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx330\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Keichou Flowerpots
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:32.13,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh man, that English teacher just wouldn't shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:35.39,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's because you were sleeping in his class, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You were asleep, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this is so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had three straight losses to Mitani,\Nmaybe I'll ditch the Go club today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.65,Sai,,0,0,0,,What!? Hikaru you can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.15,0:02:51.32,Sai,,0,0,0,,You said you were going to train because you\Nlost 3-0 to Kaiou in the last tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:54.53,Sai,,0,0,0,,Tsutsui-san's waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.45,Sai,,0,0,0,,Come on, Hikaru. Akari-chan must be waiting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry bout that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your fault for walking there\Nwithout paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!? I think it's because\Nyou guys suck too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you trying to hit the ball!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I can do better, even\Nthough I'm in the Go club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? Give it your best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll blast a homer and get rid of some stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:24.85,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! What are you doing with that stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! This is the baseball team's pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.06,Sai,,0,0,0,,Oh! He threw a small ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.82,Sai,,0,0,0,,Oh! Wow! Wow! The ball went straight in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared now? Go club members\Nshould stay away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai! Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still only one strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit it in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:03:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally a foul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:22.53,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fad(334,334)}Note: Silence a crying baby is a Japanese idiom. Meaning someone is so\Nhorrifying that it would cause even a baby to stop crying in fear of upsetting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaga! Who can silence a crying baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! This is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,K... Kaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea as to what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry. It's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your trophies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.93,Background,,0,0,0,,That junk doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This? What about this teacup?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my beloved teacup that I used all the\Ntime! It's very important, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Fine! I'll bring you another one tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.86,Background,,0,0,0,,You'll be in for it if you get me crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:05.78,Background,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of teacups would Kaga like anyways?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have 200 yen left from my allowance, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:16.30,Sai,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.38,Sai,,0,0,0,,A teacup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:19.76,Background,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.80,Background,,0,0,0,,What!? 5,000yen!? That's so expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Let's look somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:28.85,Background,,0,0,0,,What!? This is a Keichou flowerpot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:30.39,Sai,,0,0,0,,Keichou flowerpot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,During the early years of the Edo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Keichou period, there was a brilliant\Npotter called Sanwa Yaemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowerpots were Yaemon's specialties right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why we call flowerpots made\Nby Yaemon, Keichou flowerpots, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know a lot about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:59.09,Background,,0,0,0,,It really is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:02.34,Background,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful, but also elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.22,Background,,0,0,0,,You have a good eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.67,Background,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rare find. How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.27,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! This is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:22.40,Sai,,0,0,0,,Torajirou knew enough about Yaemon's flowerpots\Nto have his own unique views on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.74,Sai,,0,0,0,,So I am familiar with several of them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:26.57,Sai,,0,0,0,,But, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.82,Sai,,0,0,0,,The Indigo is rather bland,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.79,Sai,,0,0,0,,The finish is uneven...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.62,Sai,,0,0,0,,The shape doesn't have the class\Nthat a work of Yaemon would.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,1,500,000, and not a yen less.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,1,500,000!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For this fake!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.89,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I see it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.80,Background,,0,0,0,,No! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-It's not my fault! I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.82,Sai,,0,0,0,,You sure are breaking a lot of things today, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be a child, but I'm going\Nto have to make you pay for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,1,500,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.53,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! Come on, tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a Keichou flowerpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been saying that, but do you\Neven know what a real one is like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... umm... ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:23.55,Sai,,0,0,0,,The Indigo is more brilliant, and...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Indigo is more brilliant, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The finish isn't this uneven, and most importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The shape doesn't have class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You have good eyes, for a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:44.99,Sai,,0,0,0,,He...! He looks just like a toad\Nwhen he smiles! I hate toads!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this!? It's a fake!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The 1,500,000 was a lie!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I said too much in front of the foolish target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish target!? Are you talking about me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:08:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I like people who have an eye for things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.50,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! Don't get liked by people like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's your fault that he has taken a liking to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,After doing this business for awhile, you start\ndeveloping an eye for people as well as for things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid. There are only two types\Nof people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people who have an eye for things, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,idiots who don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, I won't make you pay for that\Nin respect to your knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so they said it was worth 1,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You happily paid 200,000 for it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:58.23,Background,,0,0,0,,You should feel ashamed for not being able to tell\Nthe difference rather than calling to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like you who can't even judge the\Nvalue of things shouldn't have meddled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It is grandpa's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you're doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Keep your hands off the merchandise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:27.63,Background,,0,0,0,,But this is grandpa's! It was stolen six months ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:39.02,Sai,,0,0,0,,That....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.74,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! This flowerpot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it was stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We got broken into...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of my business. Someone\Ncame to sell it and I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.42,Sai,,0,0,0,,I've seen this flowerpot before\Nin the palace in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:17.81,Sai,,0,0,0,,That one time when Torajirou\Nand I went there to tutor go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.14,Sai,,0,0,0,,It has to be the flowerpot we saw then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.31,Sai,,0,0,0,,A Keichou flowerpot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's genuine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be a cheap pot, but there's\Nno reason for me to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it's a cheap pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.24,Sai,,0,0,0,,There's a secret to this flowerpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:43.83,Sai,,0,0,0,,This man... he hasn't realized what the secret is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me money if you want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,100,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:55.51,Sai,,0,0,0,,I told you. I can't stand toads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,100,000!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But you just said it's a cheap pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In my store I decide the prices for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's up to the customer\Nwhether to buy it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:08.36,Background,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's grandpa's!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you're doing!? Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! She broke this teacup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:30.04,Sai,,0,0,0,,But you pushed her into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:33.51,Sai,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you worry whether she's all right or not!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly have courage when\Nthis guy's not smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This teacup is worth 50,000! 50,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'm highly doubtful that\Nit's actually worth that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai. Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.94,Sai,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about teacups.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.02,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:55.95,Background,,0,0,0,,A Go board?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:57.40,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.53,Sai,,0,0,0,,It seems like this person plays Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.62,Background,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on little girl, pay up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,50,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:08.96,Background,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use talking to you about it, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me your home phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.47,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, you play Go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to play me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You play Go as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play a game, with the price\Nof the teacup on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you even more now. All right,\NI accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really play Go like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:51.54,Background,,0,0,0,,This person has a fifth-dan certificate!\NYou can't play him at Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That certificate isn't fake, it's totally genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second, I'm not sure now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to play if you're scared, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.26,Sai,,0,0,0,,Me!? Get scared!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so that you know, I'm not going to take it easy\Non you. I said that I took a liking to you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I HATE self-righteous, arrogant little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.53,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai, you can't stand his face,\Nright? Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:29.91,Sai,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. He won't be smiling at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.20,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm playing first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile since I last played black.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to play now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.22,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.56,Sai,,0,0,0,,16-17, Komoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:54.39,Sai,,0,0,0,,18-5, Hane!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:57.35,Sai,,0,0,0,,8-18, Kaketsugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.04,Sai,,0,0,0,,2-17, Ate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,W-Why is he so good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one sided...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely one sided... I don't play\Nvery well, but even I can see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.33,Background,,0,0,0,,The overwhelming difference in skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:56.83,Background,,0,0,0,,This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost... how could I lose...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:13.39,Sai,,0,0,0,,To see that old flowerpot again at a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.48,Sai,,0,0,0,,I hear the palace was short on funds at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:22.06,Sai,,0,0,0,,Did someone in the palace\Nat the time secretly sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.61,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yaemon's flowerpot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:30.83,Sai,,0,0,0,,Both Torajirou and I were so awed by its\Nbeauty, that our desire to play Go faded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:35.16,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, the secret to that flowerpot is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.17,Background,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch stones with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your captured stones, too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll switch sides and continue this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And, if I manage to turn the game around,\Nwill you return that flowerpot to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.48,Background,,0,0,0,,Turn this game that I resigned from around!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can do that!\NHow dare you act so cocky!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.53,Background,,0,0,0,,Give it your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.87,Sai,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:16.41,Background,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.13,Sai,,0,0,0,,16-2, Keima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.03,Sai,,0,0,0,,3-9, Cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.77,Thinking,,0,0,0,,T-Th-This...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.31,Thinking,,0,0,0,,is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that flowerpot back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!? He's giving it back to me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just who is he!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you that worthless flowerpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister. Can you pour the water in\Nthat flower vase into the flowerpot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to pour water in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa just kept it stored away, and never\Nused it because it was too precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd give it to me when I got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.33,Sai,,0,0,0,,To be able to see this flowerpot again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.13,Sai,,0,0,0,,What deep joy I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:34.68,Sai,,0,0,0,,This flowerpot has, like me, survived\Nthrough a long period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:44.94,Background,,0,0,0,,Flowers are starting to appear\Nat the bottom of the pot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A flowerpot is only a flowerpot\Nif it has flowers in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposedly Yaemon's final masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a special finish on it, so it looks\Ndifferent from his other works
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've heard of it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is that legendary...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't there only two types of people in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:27.81,Background,,0,0,0,,People who know the value of\Nthings, and idiots who don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're an idiot who doesn't\Nknow the value of things, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Case closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:19:59.76,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.27,Sai,,0,0,0,,Haven't we forgotten something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:08.44,Background,,0,0,0,,Kaga's teacup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.36,Background,,0,0,0,,This thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! It's called a Keichou teacup, and it's\Na masterpiece from the early Edo period!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Those pictures of swimming fish were drawn by the\Ngenius Yaemon, who was said to draw like a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! It's beautiful, and its shape\Nis absolutely marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very rare work.
