Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou, you're the only one who has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:05.45,Background,,0,0,0,,From what I hear, Isumi-san went to China\Nto play against Chinese players.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san went to China?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:12.25,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go back to Japan when I'm still\Ndissatisfied about losing a game I could have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.76,0:23:25.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't if I want to take the pro exams with confidence!
